1.download it and anslyze it

2.know if our ip addr is from IS (iceland) , we will be redirected to http://south , else http://north

3.so we need to use proxy to connect it

4.i use tor

download => sudo apt install tor
run it => tor
check alive => curl -i --socks5-hostname 127.0.0.1:9050 https://check.torproject.org/api/ip
=> cd /etc/tor
=> vim torrc (if you want to add something , you need to be root) , plus "ExitNodes {is}" , "StrictNodes 1"
check your proxy ip => curl --socks5-hostname 127.0.0.1:9050 https://ipinfo.io/json
connect it => curl --socks5-hostname 127.0.0.1:9050 http://lonely-island.picoctf.net:59316/

